		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="91997"></a><b>Odibil Lauxes</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Arch Mage<br /><img src="images/avatars/21153198203e6ac8599f9ef.gif" alt="" border="0" /><br /><br />Joined: 18 Feb 2002<br />Posts: 413<br /></span><br /></td>
		<td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=91997&amp;sid=cce88950f15aa675ce01fe8711752b4a#91997"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Sun Oct 05, 2003 8:23 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Veil of Abandon (Experimental AA)</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=91997&amp;sid=cce88950f15aa675ce01fe8711752b4a"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
