				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Everyone has missed the point.
<br />

<br />
The above suggestion is completely different than merely lowering you on the hatelist, it is meant to <span style="font-weight: bold">remove you from the hatelist completely</span>, much like Feign Death, without the ability to remain feigned.
<br />

<br />
Situations where wipes are inevitable, green-cons are scowling at you in the way of your main objective, and trash clearing becomes unnecessarily tedious, this skill would be a Godsend. Consider this the 'living' version of Feign Death, nothing more.
<br />

<br />
However, lowering the recast time to maybe 4 minutes could make this a viable concussion spell on named encounters, come to think of it. Shoot two birds with one stone.<br />_________________<br /><center><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal">::: <b>Master</b> | <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90407" target="_blank">Odibil Lauxes</a> | <b>Arch Convoker</b> :::<br>That which ordinary men are fit for, I am qualified in;<br>and within the best of me is <a href="http://www.diligenceguild.com" target="_blank">DILIGENCE</a>.</span></center></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
